<section xml:id="ch-2-section-1" xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude">
    <title>Python script attempt</title>
    
    <exercise>
        <statement>
            <p>This problem requires the user to write a Python program to calculate the product of two numbers.</p>
            <p>Instructions:</p>
            <ol>
                <li>Prompt the user to enter two numbers.</li>
                <li>Calculate the product of the two numbers.</li>
                <li>Display the product to the user.</li>
            </ol>
            <p>Here is a code snippet as a reference:</p>
        </statement>
        <program interactive="activecode" language="python">
            <p>Write a Python program to calculate the product of two numbers.</p>

            <codeblock interactive="activecode" language="python">
                <![CDATA[
                # Python program to calculate the product of two numbers
                
                # Input the first number
                num1 = float(input("Enter the first number: "))
                
                # Input the second number
                num2 = float(input("Enter the second number: "))
                
                # Calculate the product
                product = num1 * num2
                
                # Display the product
                print("The product of", num1, "and", num2, "is", product)
                ]]>

            </codeblock>
        </program>
    </exercise>
</section>